    <item>
      <title>给自己看的乱七八糟有用的东西</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E4%B9%B1%E4%B8%83%E5%85%AB%E7%B3%9F/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>qwqdhs@outlook.com (qwq的红石/屿寻sama)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/%E4%B9%B1%E4%B8%83%E5%85%AB%E7%B3%9F/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>给自己看的乱七八糟有用的东西</h1><p>作者：qwq的红石/屿寻sama（qwqdhs@outlook.com）</p>
        
          <h2 id="输出数组最大小值">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e8%be%93%e5%87%ba%e6%95%b0%e7%bb%84%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%a7%e5%b0%8f%e5%80%bc"></a>
输出数组最大（小）值
</h2><div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kt">int</span> <span class="n">a</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">};</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cout</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;*</span><span class="n">max</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">min</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="n">_element</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">begin</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">),</span><span class="n">end</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">));</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">//输出5(1)
</span></span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h2 id="保留x位小数">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%bf%9d%e7%95%99x%e4%bd%8d%e5%b0%8f%e6%95%b0"></a>
保留x位小数
</h2><div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cout</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">fixed</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">setprecision</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">a</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h2 id="最大公约数">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%a7%e5%85%ac%e7%ba%a6%e6%95%b0"></a>
最大公约数
</h2><div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">//需要C++17标准
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">gcd</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h2 id="三个数比大小">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%b8%89%e4%b8%aa%e6%95%b0%e6%af%94%e5%a4%a7%e5%b0%8f"></a>
三个数比大小
</h2><div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">//直接用std max和min就行
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">//C++11标准
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">max</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">c</span><span class="p">});</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">min</span><span class="p">({</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">c</span><span class="p">});</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h2 id="vector去重">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#vector%e5%8e%bb%e9%87%8d"></a>
vector去重
</h2><div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">//需要事先排序
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">erase</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">unique</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">begin</span><span class="p">(),</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">end</span><span class="p">()),</span> <span class="n">a</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">end</span><span class="p">());</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h3 id="工作原理">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%b7%a5%e4%bd%9c%e5%8e%9f%e7%90%86"></a>
工作原理
</h3><p>unique:将相邻的重复元素移动到容器末尾，并返回去重后第一个无效元素的迭代器。</p>
<p>erase:删除从 unique 返回的迭代器到容器末尾的所有无效元素。</p>
<h2 id="string和int互转">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#string%e5%92%8cint%e4%ba%92%e8%bd%ac"></a>
string和int互转
</h2><div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">//C++11标准
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">to_string</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">num</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-07-20首发于<a href='http://localhost:1313/'>红石的个人博客</a>，最后修改于2026-07-20</p>]]>
      </description>
      
        <category>技术</category>
      
    </item>
    
    

    <item>
      <title>给自己看的pair用法</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/pair%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jul 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>qwqdhs@outlook.com (qwq的红石/屿寻sama)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/pair%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>给自己看的pair用法</h1><p>作者：qwq的红石/屿寻sama（qwqdhs@outlook.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="主要内容">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e4%b8%bb%e8%a6%81%e5%86%85%e5%ae%b9"></a>
主要内容
</h1><h2 id="pair">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#pair"></a>
Pair
</h2><h3 id="语法">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e8%af%ad%e6%b3%95"></a>
语法
</h3><p>默认用法</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">pair</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="err">类型</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="err">类型</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="err">变量名</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>结合vector的用法</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">vector</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">pair</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="err">类型</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="err">类型</span><span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="err">变量名</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">大小</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h3 id="eg">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#eg"></a>
e.g:
</h3><div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">cin</span><span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="n">n</span> <span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">vector</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">pair</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="kt">int</span><span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="n">farmers</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">n</span><span class="p">);</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h2 id="排序我指vector-pair的sort排序">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%8e%92%e5%ba%8f%e6%88%91%e6%8c%87vector-pair%e7%9a%84sort%e6%8e%92%e5%ba%8f"></a>
排序(我指vector pair的sort排序)
</h2><h3 id="语法-1">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e8%af%ad%e6%b3%95-1"></a>
语法
</h3><p>默认（从小到大）</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">sort</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">变量名</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">begin</span><span class="p">(),</span><span class="err">变量名</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">end</span><span class="p">());</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>从大到小</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">sort</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">变量名</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">begin</span><span class="p">(),</span><span class="err">变量名</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">end</span><span class="p">(),</span><span class="n">greater</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">pair</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="p">());</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p><strong>注意！默认排序按 first 升序，若 first 相等则按 second 升序。</strong></p>
<p>按照pair中的数据进行排序</p>
<p>①按second升序</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">sort</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">变量名</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">begin</span><span class="p">(),</span><span class="err">变量名</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">end</span><span class="p">(),[](</span><span class="k">auto</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="k">auto</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">a</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">second</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">second</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">});</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><p>②按second降序</p>
<div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">sort</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="err">变量名</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">begin</span><span class="p">(),</span><span class="err">变量名</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">end</span><span class="p">(),[](</span><span class="k">auto</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">a</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="k">auto</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">a</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">second</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="n">b</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">second</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">});</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h1 id="相关内容">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e7%9b%b8%e5%85%b3%e5%86%85%e5%ae%b9"></a>
相关内容
</h1><h2 id="结构化绑定">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e7%bb%93%e6%9e%84%e5%8c%96%e7%bb%91%e5%ae%9a"></a>
结构化绑定
</h2><h3 id="语法-2">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e8%af%ad%e6%b3%95-2"></a>
语法
</h3><div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">for</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">auto</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">y</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="n">v</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="c1">//使用x和y
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div><h3 id="结合pair的结构化绑定eg">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e7%bb%93%e5%90%88pair%e7%9a%84%e7%bb%93%e6%9e%84%e5%8c%96%e7%bb%91%e5%ae%9aeg"></a>
结合pair的结构化绑定e.g
</h3><div class="highlight"><div class="chroma">
<table class="lntable"><tr><td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code><span class="lnt">1
</span><span class="lnt">2
</span><span class="lnt">3
</span><span class="lnt">4
</span><span class="lnt">5
</span><span class="lnt">6
</span><span class="lnt">7
</span><span class="lnt">8
</span><span class="lnt">9
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp"><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="n">vector</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="n">pair</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">string</span><span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span><span class="n">v</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="p">{{</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#34;apple&#34;</span><span class="p">},{</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#34;banana&#34;</span><span class="p">},{</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="s">&#34;cherry&#34;</span><span class="p">}};</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  <span class="k">for</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="k">auto</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">y</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">:</span><span class="n">v</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="n">cout</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class="s">&#34;: &#34;</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">y</span><span class="o">&lt;&lt;</span><span class="n">endl</span><span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="c1">// 输出：
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="c1">// 1: apple
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="c1">// 2: banana
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="c1">// 3: cherry
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span>
</span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-07-20首发于<a href='http://localhost:1313/'>红石的个人博客</a>，最后修改于2026-07-20</p>]]>
